column5: This extremely novel taco shop comes complete with a gold “Champions Booth” where you can eat with full service if you make a reservation. Mexican wrestling or “Lucha libre” paraphernalia is all around the taco shop and there is always a Mexican wrestling b-film playing on the tv. The food, naturally, is suited for champions.
column6: Lucha Libre (Mexican Wrestling) Themed Taco Shop.
column8: 1810 W. Washingon Street; San Diego, California, 92103; United States
